<section class="origin-section">
	<div class="origin-label-row">
		<span class="section-number">02 — ORIGIN STORY</span>
	</div>

	<div class="origin-layout">
		<div class="origin-image-col">
			<img
				src="/images/hedgehogReadingBook.jpeg"
				alt="A hedgehog reading a book"
				class="origin-image"
			/>
		</div>

		<div class="origin-text-col">
			<h2 class="origin-title">The PorkyProductions Origin Story</h2>
			<div class="h-rule" style="max-width: 52px; margin-bottom: 2rem;"></div>
			<div class="origin-body">
				<p>Our story begins in 2017, when our founders, Tristan and Ryan, met in school. They became friends and eventually discovered that they could make a website using Google Sites. What better thing to make a website about than a hedgehog pencil sharpener Tristan had named "Porky".</p>
				<p>After PorkyPictures.inc was created, many other websites followed: PorkySchool.edu, PorkyPizza.eat, and <abbr title="PorkyBlackHolesThatWillDestroyTheEntireUniverseSoYouProbablyShouldntUseThe.com.com.inc">PBHTWDTEUSYPSUT.c.c.i</abbr>. Porky had developed a cult following.</p>
				<p>Unfortunately, a disgusting hater stole the pencil sharpener and destroyed it. During his last moments, Porky transferred into a hedgehog plush, where he resides to this day.</p>
				<p>The old websites were archived and consolidated into one company — PorkyProductions, the site you're visiting now.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

